---
import HiddenGrammarLayout from '../../layouts/HiddenGrammarLayout.astro';
---

<HiddenGrammarLayout
  title="Where do you want to start?"
  description="Pick the path that fits. Each one surfaces the tools most useful for where you are."
>
  <div class="hg-page">

    <div class="start-wrap">

      <div class="start-header">
        <h1 class="start-title">What are you here to do?</h1>
        <p class="start-intro">Pick the one that fits. Each path surfaces the tools most useful for where you are.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="start-cards">

        <a href="/hidden-grammar/for/artist" class="start-card start-card--artist">
          <span class="start-card-label">Working artist</span>
          <p class="start-card-body">You're mid-process, or you just finished something, and you want to know what it's actually doing — not what it means, but what it's doing. Where the eye goes. What's holding and what's sliding past.</p>
          <p class="start-card-body">That's a different question than most feedback gives you. Art Lab is built around it.</p>
          <span class="start-card-cta">Show me the studio tools →</span>
        </a>

        <a href="/hidden-grammar/for/curious" class="start-card start-card--curious">
          <span class="start-card-label">Just curious</span>
          <p class="start-card-body">You don't need a reason. You saw something—in a museum, online, somewhere—and it did something to you, and you want to know what.</p>
          <p class="start-card-body">Or you made something just for the pleasure of it, and you're curious what it's actually doing.</p>
          <p class="start-card-body">No agenda required. Start here and see what comes back.</p>
          <span class="start-card-cta">Browse the tools →</span>
        </a>

        <a href="/hidden-grammar/for/educator" class="start-card start-card--edu">
          <span class="start-card-label">Educator, docent, presenter</span>
          <p class="start-card-body">You're standing in front of a work — or you will be, next Thursday, with a group of people who didn't necessarily choose to be there. You need something concrete to point at. Not interpretation. Not art-speak. Something you can actually say.</p>
          <p class="start-card-body">There are tools here built specifically for that.</p>
          <span class="start-card-cta">Show me the teaching tools →</span>
        </a>

      </div>

      <div class="start-caution">
        <h2 class="start-caution-title">One thing before you pick a tool</h2>
        <p class="start-caution-body">Art Lab makes things legible that were previously invisible. That's useful. It can also, if you're not careful, turn creating into a performance review.</p>
        <p class="start-caution-body">If you're here to see your choices more clearly—to tighten, strengthen, understand what's working—it's for you. But if creating is mostly about pleasure or flow or finding your way, be careful. Once you start measuring, it's hard to stop. The measuring can become the point.</p>
        <p class="start-caution-body">Some artists will call this reductive. They're not wrong—any analysis reduces a work. The question is whether what remains after the reduction is useful to you.</p>
        <a href="/hidden-grammar/analysis-worth" class="start-caution-link">Does analysis destroy an artwork? The full answer →</a>
        <p class="start-caution-kicker">Know what you came for.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="start-footer">
        <a href="/hidden-grammar" class="start-back">← Back to Art Lab</a>
      </div>

    </div>

  </div>
</HiddenGrammarLayout>

<style>
  .start-wrap {
    max-width: 860px;
    padding: 2.5rem 0;
  }

  .start-header {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .start-title {
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    color: #0f172a;
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    line-height: 1.15;
  }

  .start-intro {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: #64748b;
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .start-cards {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 10px;
  }

  .start-card {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0;
    padding: 1.25rem 1.375rem;
    border-radius: 10px;
    border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: border-color 0.15s ease, box-shadow 0.15s ease;
    background: #ffffff;
  }

  .start-card:hover {
    border-color: #94a3b8;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
  }

  .start-card--artist  { border-left: 3px solid #7c3aed; }
  .start-card--curious { border-left: 3px solid #d97706; }
  .start-card--edu     { border-left: 3px solid #059669; }

  .start-card-label {
    display: block;
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 0.625rem;
  }

  .start-card--artist  .start-card-label { color: #6d28d9; }
  .start-card--curious .start-card-label { color: #b45309; }
  .start-card--edu     .start-card-label { color: #047857; }

  .start-card-body {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    color: #475569;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
  }

  .start-card-body:last-of-type {
    margin-bottom: 0.875rem;
  }

  .start-card-cta {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    align-self: flex-start;
  }

  .start-card--artist  .start-card-cta { color: #6d28d9; }
  .start-card--curious .start-card-cta { color: #b45309; }
  .start-card--edu     .start-card-cta { color: #047857; }

  .start-caution {
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
    padding: 1.5rem 1.75rem;
    background: #fffbeb;
    border: 1px solid #fde68a;
    border-left: 3px solid #f59e0b;
    border-radius: 0 10px 10px 0;
  }

  .start-caution-title {
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #92400e;
    margin: 0 0 0.875rem;
  }

  .start-caution-body {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    color: #78350f;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
  }

  .start-caution-link {
    color: #92400e;
    margin-top: 0.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .start-caution-link:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  .start-caution-kicker {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-style: italic;
    color: #92400e;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .start-footer {
    margin-top: 2rem;
    padding-top: 1.5rem;
    border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
  }

  .start-back {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: #64748b;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .start-back:hover {
    color: #334155;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .start-cards {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 540px) {
    .start-cards {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
